cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language generation. It also involves neural network computation, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses images as input, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper proposes a novel architecture, which could also fall under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
